E-commerce Platform
This project is a simple e-commerce platform built with Django that provides product browsing, shopping cart functionality, and integrates with Stripe for payment processing. 
Users can browse products, add them to a cart, and proceed to checkout for secure payments. 
The project uses session-based cart functionality and Stripeâ€™s API for managing payments.

Features
Product Listing: Users can browse through available products.
Shopping Cart: Users can add products to their cart, update quantities, and remove items.
Stripe Payment Integration: Secure payment process using Stripe API for creating checkout sessions.
Session-based Cart: Cart functionality is session-based for both anonymous and authenticated users (authentication is not implemented).

Installation Guide

1. git clone https://github.com/your-username/ecommerce-project.git
2. cd ecommerce-project
3. pip install django stripe
4. export STRIPE_TEST_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key
5. export STRIPE_TEST_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key
6. python manage.py migrate
7. python manage.py runserver
